00:20:27.072 --> 00:20:32.279
Final answer?
Boy, you are right.

00:20:32.279 --> 00:20:36.599
Top one is greater.
Recitation eight.

00:20:36.599 --> 00:20:43.200
It is greater because the
effective charge in boron plus

00:20:43.200 --> 00:20:50.279
is larger than it is in boron.
There are fewer electrons for

00:20:50.279 --> 00:20:55.200
shielding.
The effective charge is larger.

00:20:55.200 --> 00:21:02.805
That binding energy is greater.
Or, that ionization energy

00:21:02.805 --> 00:21:06.690
here, the way I write it,
