00:21:22.661 --> 00:21:28.057
as we go across it,
what happens to that ionization

00:21:28.057 --> 00:21:31.125
energy?
Wait.

00:21:31.125 --> 00:21:36.750
Are we in position?
Ready?

00:21:36.750 --> 00:21:39.000
Launch.

00:21:45.000 --> 00:21:49.878
Recitation five.
What happens to the ionization

00:21:49.878 --> 00:21:54.333
energy as you go across the
